OL,3,CCouncil given formal notice to improve
OL,4,Cafter #100k trips to French Riviera
OL,6,FA council has been served with a
OL,7,Fformal notice and told it must improve
OL,8,Fits spending - after spending nearly
OL,9,F#300,000 on trips to the French
OL,10,FRiviera.
OL,12,FThe Ministry of Housing, Communities
OL,13,Fand Local Government said "urgent
OL,14,Faction" was needed as ministers remain
OL,15,Fconcerned about Dudley Council's
OL,16,Fability to "comply with its best value
OL,17,Fduty".
