OL,3,CCouncil given formal notice to improve
OL,4,Cafter #100k trips to French Riviera
OL,6,FIt said the council has faced issues
OL,7,Fhistorically in "delivering planned
OL,8,Fsavings" and continues to have
OL,9,F"significant value for money
OL,10,Fweaknesses".
OL,12,FDudley Council came under fire in 2022
OL,13,Fafter it was revealed that it spent a
OL,14,Ftotal of #279,155 for three trips
OL,15,Fabroad - two were cancelled because of
OL,16,FCovid.
OL,18,FBut the council said the one trip that
OL,19,Fdid happen was a net benefit, helping
OL,20,Fthem secure #50 million of investment
OL,21,Ffor the borough.
