OL,3,CCouncil given formal notice to improve
OL,4,Cafter #100k trips to French Riviera
OL,6,FCouncil leader Patrick Harley denied
OL,7,Fthe fact that notice was sent because
OL,8,Fthe council had wasted money, and said
OL,9,Fthe Government were instead
OL,10,Facknowledging its financial
OL,11,Fdifficulties.
OL,13,FHe said: "The sanction against us is
OL,14,Fthe lowest the government could do...
OL,15,FBut I welcome added scrutiny. We are
OL,16,Fdelivering everything they are
OL,17,Freferring to. We have to do more to
OL,18,Fkeep Dudley on a stable footing."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/9
