OL,3,CCouncil given formal notice to improve
OL,4,Cafter #100k trips to French Riviera
OL,6,FHe added the investment they have
OL,7,Fbrought in has allowed them to reopen
OL,8,Fthe Dudley Museum and helped them
OL,9,Fstart planning a new ice rink in the
OL,10,Fborough.
OL,12,FCllr Harley blamed the financial
OL,13,Ftrouble the council has had in part on
OL,14,Fthe "unbelievably obscene" cost of
OL,15,Fadult social care and children's
OL,16,Fservices, but says their finances are
OL,17,Fnow on a much firmer footing.
