OL,3,CCouncil given formal notice to improve
OL,4,Cafter #100k trips to French Riviera
OL,6,FIn a later statement, Cllr Harley
OL,7,Fadded: "The improvements we have made
OL,8,Fover a short period of time are
OL,9,Fincredible and I very much welcome the
OL,10,Fbest value notice as an opportunity to
OL,11,Foutline that to the government.
OL,13,F"It will allow us to give that cast
OL,14,Firon guarantee that we are already far
OL,15,Fdown the track and will continue to
OL,16,Fimprove.
OL,18,F"From the very beginning we have
OL,19,Fwelcomed scrutiny as part of a fresh
OL,20,Fstart and this notice adds to that.
OL,26,@oD@HOUzD@AOU
