OL,3,CCouncil given formal notice to improve
OL,4,Cafter #100k trips to French Riviera
OL,6,F"We recognise that there is still more
OL,7,Fwork to do and we will approach that
OL,8,Fwith the same drive as we have with
OL,9,Four successes to date."
OL,11,FHarley added: "So far we have set a
OL,12,Fbalanced budget which stops any more
OL,13,Ftalk of potential financial crisis and
OL,14,Fwe are welcoming the first new faces
OL,15,Fin a new-look senior management team
OL,16,Fto build on the improvements we have
OL,17,Falready achieved.
