OL,3,CCouncil given formal notice to improve
OL,4,Cafter #100k trips to French Riviera
OL,6,FMeamwhile, Pete Lowe, the leader of
OL,7,Fthe Black County Party, welcomed the
OL,8,Fformal notice and the greater scrutiny
OL,9,Faround the council's spending.
OL,11,FHe denied that the council's trip to
OL,12,Fthe Riviera was value for money,
OL,13,Fsaying: "If you look at the hundreds
OL,14,Fof thousands of pounds of residents'
OL,15,Fmoney that was spent and wasted by
OL,16,Fpoliticians in Dudley, that was spent
OL,17,Fand wasted on going on a junket to
OL,18,FCannes or the one and a half million
OL,19,Fthat was spent on Brookes Bar, then I
OL,20,Fdon't think you could find anyone that
OL,21,Fsays that's value for money."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/9
