OL,6,FCllr Lowe added: "Wasting hundreds of
OL,7,Fthousands of pounds on trips to France
OL,8,Fis not in the interest of value for
OL,9,Fmoney for people in the community.
OL,11,F"They go to France while our community
OL,12,Fcentres are closed, while our dementia
OL,13,Fservices are closed, while services
OL,14,Ffor the hard-working people of Dudley
OL,15,Fare eroded.
